Package views.handler

Class BaseScreenHandler

java.lang.Object
views.handler.FXMLScreenHandler
views.handler.BaseScreenHandler
Direct Known Subclasses:
BikeDetailsScreenHandler, GetBarcodeReturnBikeScreenHandler, GetBarcodeScreenHandler, HomeScreenHandler, PaymentConfirmHandler, PaymentFormHandler, PaymentResultHandler, RentalOrderConfirmScreenHandler, ReturnBikeScreenHandler, SearchResultScreenHandler, StationDetailsScreenHandler
public abstract class BaseScreenHandler
extends FXMLScreenHandler
The abstract class BaseScreenHandler provides basic methods to work on a screen handler. All the screen handlers must extend this class.
Since:
1.0
Author:
